def transform_defi(self, ns, row) -> list:
    """ID: bd8b8a39-013f-4fcb-98e6-1423c4b97cef"""
    defi: Definition = self.defs.get(ns)
    transDefiNames = []
    for point_ns in defi.get_name_pointer(row):
        transDefiNames.append(point_ns)
    return transDefiNames
